    SUBA[["Skill-backed subagents (isolated child context)<br/>all custom profile templates render prefix.txt preamble before role instructions<br/>agent-review: native harness discovery + role-specific runtime contracts<br/>PR necessity/intent gate when required → concurrency-safe Cursor/Copilot GPT+Opus workers · Claude Task reviewer opus/sonnet · Codex spawn_agent review-worker x2 · Gemini review-gemini-pro/flash · Amp Task x2<br/>review-controller (Pi): PR necessity gate when required → fan-out openrouter opus:off + gpt-5.5:xhigh → live-ui → inline/delegated findings audit → pending-review reconciliation → act<br/>reviewer lanes return candidate findings + verification_needed; controller owns sticky verification ledger + mutation/contention serial checks<br/>local adopted/assigned PR changes that need PR intent route through PR intent audit before fixes<br/>pr-necessity-auditor→agent-review/pr-necessity-auditor contract + review/pr_common<br/>findings-auditor/post-review→review/judging_core 4-dim<br/>live-ui-review returns applicability/comparison/screenshot handoff/target-packet/branch/runtime/data blocker; Elastic/Kibana concrete targets live in elastic-domain overlay<br/>change-auditor→light-review (proportional in-place audit)<br/>skills stay the source of truth"]]:::claude
